22  package com.github.talbotgui.psl.socle.commun.oidc.dto;
23  
24  import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonIgnoreProperties;
25  import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty;
26  
27  /** Classe image de la reponse OIDC renvoyée par le fournisseur d'identité OIDC. */
28  @JsonIgnoreProperties(ignoreUnknown = true)
29  public record ReponseTokenOIDC(@JsonProperty("access_token") String accessToken, @JsonProperty("expires_in") String expiresIn,
30  		@JsonProperty("refresh_expires_in") String refreshExpiresIn, @JsonProperty("refresh_token") String refreshToken,
31  		@JsonProperty("token_type") String tokenType, @JsonProperty("id_token") String idToken, @JsonProperty("session_state") String sessionState,
32  		@JsonProperty("scope") String scope) {
33  }
